r":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man does not accuse another man of wickedness or unbelief but that it will be turned against him, if his companion is innocent.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6045 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7655,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/cursing-killing-muslim-kufr\/","url_meta":{"origin":7642,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Muslims: Cursing him is wicked, killing is unbelief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDisparaging a Muslim is an act of wickedness, and fighting him is an act of unbelief.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7076, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 64 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/19\/takfir-wrongful-accusation-backfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":7642,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Takfir: False charges of unbelief backfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a man calls his brother an unbeliever, it turns against at least one of them.\u00a0Either the accused is as he claimed, or else the charge will turn against him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6104, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/do-not-curse-lord-of-time\/","url_meta":{"origin":7642,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Do not curse time, Allah is Time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: The son of Adam insults Me. He curses time, but I am time, for in My hand are the night and day.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4826, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2246 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1809,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/06\/murder-leads-unbelief\/","url_meta":{"origin":7642,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Killing: The Prophet warns bloodshed leads to unbelief","